{
  "text": "We estimate the relaxation time \u03bb of our liquid using the Zimm estimate \u03bb Zimm \u2248 0.03 s and L Char \u2248 12 \u00b5m for our channels; see Ref. [CITATION_1] . The mixing efficiency is found by measuring the homogeneity of a fluid domain [27] , and here is calculated using the first moment mixing index",
